          issues_1: "Some downloadable materials, especially presentations and PDF files, may not be fully prepared in accordance with accessibility requirements.",
          issues_2: "Embedded content or links to external services such as LinkedIn, Facebook, YouTube or partner websites may have limitations outside COVE Polska's control.",
          issues_3: "Some project subdomains are developed independently and may require a separate accessibility review.",
          issues_4: "Older graphics or promotional materials may require alternative text or a text version.",
          dates_h2: "Publication and update dates",
          publication_date_label: "Website publication date:",
          declaration_date_label: "Statement preparation date:",
          review_date_label: "Last statement review date:",
          keyboard_h2: "Keyboard shortcuts",
          keyboard_p: "The website does not use custom keyboard shortcuts. Users can use the standard shortcuts of their browser and operating system.",
          feedback_h2: "Feedback and contact details",
          feedback_p1: "Problems with the digital accessibility of the website, subdomains or project materials can be reported to the COVE Polska activity coordinator.",
          feedback_p2: "In your report, please provide your name, contact details, the address of the page or material concerned, a description of the problem and the preferred way of receiving a response or an alternative version of the content.",
